data.description:
Country Living at its Best!!  This will be your thought when you see this 4 bedroom, 4 bathroom home with over 2900 sq ft that sits on 2.8 acres of beautiful land!!  The serenity and natural surroundings will make you feel like you are on a vacation every day.  Inside there is a huge country style kitchen with loads of cabinets and a breakfast bar.  You can enjoy your morning coffee in the breakfast room with a bay window.  The spacious greatroom has a beautiful fireplace and built-in bookshelves.  The primary bedroom is large with a walk-in closet. This bathroom has tile and a  double vanity.  Upstairs you will find 2 HUGE bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms.  You won't believe all of the extra storage areas!!  Doing laundry will be a snap in the utility room that also offers a deep sink.  If you want horses, then this home can accommodate that with the barn and fenced land.  You will love the beautiful in-ground swimming pool with a huge deck for the hot summer days ahead.  On top of all of that, the owners recently added a fabulous outdoor living area which allows for great enjoyment of summer activities while staying cool.  You will also love this area during the cooler months for watching games and enjoying a crisp Fall morning outside.   Need a workshop for those large or small projects?  This home offers a large wired workshop that will satisfy your need for a space to complete projects or just to store large items.  Other details to note:
new windows and siding added in 2019
new water heater in 2021
HVAC (upstairs) 2023 (downstairs) 2016
Pool liner 2020
fence in yard/pool 2019
Screened back porch with power shades, stamped and stained flooring 
This home offers convenience to schools, shopping and the Interstate.  So much to offer and ready for you to make this house your home!!  VA Assumable loan at 2.2%
